<TEXT>
theres no periscope and there is water 
inside but a twoman submarine built by students is mits bet to 
crack the eightminute kilometer and win the first international 
submarine race 
after months of planning and production the cigarshaped icarus 
was launched tuesday on its first voyage in the alumni pool of the 
massachusetts institute of technology 
they didnt go very fast swimmers lapped them 
