1972 when his water started tasting bad 
it smelled like sulfur he said at the same time he started 
itching and having skin problems 
the dog scratched for a week after a bath he added he 
dont imagine things 
in october 1981 the county health department advised residents 
that the well water in this area could be potentially hazardous to 
your health and you should not drink it 
