tenn to say goodbye to his son david who is making his first 
lengthy deployment 
hes excited were excited for him gary jones said 
he said his son had talked little about the explosion i think 
hes gone through the whole ordeal real good he said we didnt 
ask him too many questions 
cindy jagel wife of an iowa crewman said she was not concerned 
about the ships safety it doesnt seem to be anything that would 
happen again she said 
the damaged no 2 turret has been cleaned and painted and will be 
