barnaclestudded pipe off florida power amp lights st lucie nuclear 
plant on the atlantic coast 
it was darker than any dark ive ever seen and i tried to hold 
my arms in front of me for balance but i tumbled and bounced all 
over the sides of the pipe 
lamms trip through the plant coolingwater system ended four 
