contractor in this case has the institutional memory and the 
expertise 
the massachusetts democrat also expressed dismay over the 
pentagons inability to keep track of the consultants the absence 
of a specific definition of the term consultant and the possibility 
that these problems could result in incidents of 
conflictofinterest 
allan burman deputy administrator and acting administrator in 
the office of federal procurement policy said his agency has come 
up with a policy letter on conflictofinterest that will require a 
60day comment period 
