to you the proper information with regard to that question i want 
to know i have a right to know the american people have a right to 
know why cant i get that from you the congressman said 
burman said that with the number of broad categories it is 
difficult for consultants looking at those categories to determine 
whether they are part of the process 
its very difficult for us to get any kind of consistency he 
said 
